{"tid":309553,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺訓導越老越變態，好比薑越老越辣","createTime":"2017-07-05T06:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T17:44:07.000Z","uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c2c19ab98f850c7d56c39131b24131ee97bb9cf","tid":309553,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8361c639eaf70440339bc2c3d2b9a3aea73852da","tid":309553,"uid":116161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"正常啊，不嬲都係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4f54b08ce7ce3f937766ab9ed2cfc81c5925ab","tid":309553,"uid":120051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:43:08.000Z","msg":"六常兄做咩咁感慨呀？"},{"pid":"0a06ef503ee18415bc15ea45362130e85fa87174","tid":309553,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常啊，不嬲都係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起小學有位訓導真係好變態，雖然依家冇做"},{"pid":"010da263c1073a8e5d52cb454d1bdf0adae25d62","tid":309553,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六常兄做咩咁感慨呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n閒時回憶下過去，諗到唔少令我概嘆嘅野。原來小學食包媽咪麵可以開心半日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca86198dba83c0d3c92ecd944ab84db89cbeffd8","tid":309553,"uid":69855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"296f75e867e86220daf01f8833f39c588a879005","tid":309553,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:33:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔太同意，之後有個好後生嘅miss叫我幫佢奶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前我頭髮過眉畀佢捉<br />\n咁啱有班女仔(6,7個)打交又畀佢捉咗<br />\n結果個Miss罰我連埋佢中出晒所有人<br />\n賓周都損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e8d3a79c7713340ff974a609e1e978e47f5cf7","tid":309553,"uid":90409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:58:49.000Z","msg":"有d 好hea, 擺明做 show扮惡"},{"pid":"364d243ec6ab775e64f2480eb4d508c2c39cb848","tid":309553,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T17:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔太同意，之後有個好後生嘅miss叫我幫佢奶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前我頭髮過眉畀佢捉<br />\n咁啱有班女仔(6,7個)打交又畀佢捉咗<br />\n結果個Miss罰我連埋佢中出晒所有人<br />\n賓周都損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040d669bad9d0fbeec86a0a499474261be7e2a58","tid":309553,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T17:44:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d 好hea, 擺明做 show扮惡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小學雞嚇一嚇會瀨尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}